;
SHEET
DETERMINATION METHOD: DSSP
THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "AI" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN  6-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
A  7-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.

THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "BG" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN  6-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
A  7-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.

THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "BH" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN  6-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
